1
00:00:20,280 --> 00:00:21,680
What are you doing here?

2
00:00:23,200 --> 00:00:24,560
Sister-in-law got hurt, didn't she?

3
00:00:24,560 --> 00:00:25,960
I came to check on her.

4
00:00:27,160 --> 00:00:29,490
You're done showing your concern, right?

5
00:00:29,840 --> 00:00:30,240
Leave.

6
00:00:40,080 --> 00:00:40,880
What's wrong?

7
00:00:47,240 --> 00:00:48,520
Does your wound still hurt?

8
00:00:48,520 --> 00:00:50,600
Compared to your misunderstanding,

9
00:00:51,360 --> 00:00:54,560
my heart hurts more than the wound.

10
00:00:58,080 --> 00:01:00,880
Good thing I've figured out how to make it up to you.

11
00:01:06,080 --> 00:01:06,880
Commander.

12
00:01:07,960 --> 00:01:10,160
Th-there's an urgent military matter.

13
00:01:12,480 --> 00:01:13,320
Got it.

14
00:01:19,720 --> 00:01:20,560
Wait for me.

15
00:01:26,160 --> 00:01:27,360
He's acting strange.

16
00:01:29,000 --> 00:01:30,560
Could he be suspecting me?

17
00:01:32,200 --> 00:01:33,960
Commander, regarding the theft of the contract

18
00:01:33,960 --> 00:01:35,360
and its use to frame the Song family,

19
00:01:35,360 --> 00:01:37,120
we have traced it to a suspect.

20
00:01:42,640 --> 00:01:44,400
Keep an eye on Yao Shengsheng.

21
00:01:44,720 --> 00:01:45,520
Find out

22
00:01:45,520 --> 00:01:47,720
who she's been associating with recently.

23
00:01:47,720 --> 00:01:48,440
Yes, sir.

24
00:02:10,600 --> 00:02:11,520
Are you okay?

25
00:02:11,920 --> 00:02:12,720
You're 15 minutes later

26
00:02:12,720 --> 00:02:13,800
than we agreed.

27
00:02:13,840 --> 00:02:15,300
Someone was following me.

28
00:02:18,160 --> 00:02:20,090
The Song family is watching me too.

29
00:02:21,720 --> 00:02:22,640
I'm really sorry

30
00:02:22,640 --> 00:02:24,170
for dragging you into this.

31
00:02:24,880 --> 00:02:25,920
For safety's sake,

32
00:02:25,920 --> 00:02:27,720
why don't you leave Jiangcheng?

33
00:02:28,040 --> 00:02:29,570
What are you talking about?

34
00:02:29,640 --> 00:02:31,320
I've weathered plenty of storms.

35
00:02:31,320 --> 00:02:32,720
I can handle this easily.

36
00:02:33,880 --> 00:02:35,720
Song Huainan is ruthless.

37
00:02:36,160 --> 00:02:37,280
If he finds you,

38
00:02:37,280 --> 00:02:38,360
he won't spare you.

39
00:02:38,360 --> 00:02:39,420
That's exactly why

40
00:02:39,440 --> 00:02:41,040
I can't leave you alone

41
00:02:41,040 --> 00:02:42,500
to fight someone like him.

42
00:02:43,000 --> 00:02:45,160
Don't worry. I'll stay with you.

43
00:02:45,320 --> 00:02:46,800
Unless it's absolutely necessary

44
00:02:46,800 --> 00:02:47,960
for me to leave.

45
00:02:51,640 --> 00:02:53,160
If I can find Aunt Hong,

46
00:02:53,600 --> 00:02:54,600
doesn't that mean

47
00:02:57,680 --> 00:02:59,000
Song Qingzhou

48
00:02:59,360 --> 00:03:00,890
would never aid the wicked?

49
00:03:01,560 --> 00:03:03,480
He's different from Song Huainan.

50
00:03:03,480 --> 00:03:04,680
Regarding Aunt Hong,

51
00:03:04,720 --> 00:03:06,320
I've found out almost everything.

52
00:03:06,320 --> 00:03:07,720
I just need final confirmation.

53
00:03:07,720 --> 00:03:09,440
When the dust settles,

54
00:03:09,680 --> 00:03:11,340
I'll take the money you gave me

55
00:03:11,440 --> 00:03:12,840
and go live the high life.

56
00:03:13,680 --> 00:03:15,280
How much longer will it take?

57
00:03:18,480 --> 00:03:19,360
Three days.

58
00:03:19,880 --> 00:03:21,560
Come find me in three days.

59
00:03:23,120 --> 00:03:24,040
Wait, wait.

60
00:03:24,360 --> 00:03:25,160
It's not safe.

61
00:03:25,680 --> 00:03:27,400
We're both being watched.

62
00:03:27,840 --> 00:03:29,560
If you come here again,

63
00:03:30,920 --> 00:03:31,720
no.

64
00:03:32,400 --> 00:03:34,000
We have to go somewhere else.

65
00:03:34,360 --> 00:03:35,560
But outside,

66
00:03:36,240 --> 00:03:37,700
it might be even less safe.

67
00:03:40,680 --> 00:03:41,480
My house.

68
00:03:44,800 --> 00:03:46,329
How about the old Zhu house?

69
00:03:47,240 --> 00:03:49,600
The most dangerous place is the safest.

70
00:03:49,600 --> 00:03:51,320
Let's meet there.

71
00:03:51,520 --> 00:03:52,320
Okay.

72
00:03:53,520 --> 00:03:54,320
By the way,

73
00:03:56,120 --> 00:03:57,380
there's one more thing

74
00:03:57,440 --> 00:03:58,760
I need to tell you.

75
00:03:58,920 --> 00:04:00,320
I also heard

76
00:04:01,040 --> 00:04:03,440
that a lot of people are investigating you.

77
00:04:04,120 --> 00:04:05,360
You must be careful.

78
00:04:07,120 --> 00:04:07,920
I will.

79
00:04:20,680 --> 00:04:22,540
Today is Shengsheng's birthday.

80
00:04:22,880 --> 00:04:25,680
I've already had the servants make arrangements.

81
00:04:26,480 --> 00:04:27,320
Something came up at the military academy.

82
00:04:27,320 --> 00:04:28,520
I need to go handle it.

83
00:04:28,520 --> 00:04:29,080
Okay.

84
00:04:35,120 --> 00:04:36,720
Don't worry, Dad.

85
00:04:37,760 --> 00:04:39,560
For Sister-in-law's birthday,

86
00:04:39,600 --> 00:04:41,000
I'll be there on time.

87
00:04:42,400 --> 00:04:42,880
Good.

88
00:04:42,960 --> 00:04:44,020
Come on, let's eat.

89
00:04:50,200 --> 00:04:52,320
Marshal, we've found that person's information.

90
00:04:52,320 --> 00:04:53,040
Their surname is Lin.

91
00:04:53,040 --> 00:04:54,600
He claims to be a detective.

92
00:04:54,720 --> 00:04:55,800
Did you catch him?

93
00:04:55,880 --> 00:04:56,940
During the arrest,

94
00:04:57,560 --> 00:04:58,440
he escaped.

95
00:05:00,080 --> 00:05:01,360
But don't worry.

96
00:05:01,680 --> 00:05:02,560
He was shot.

97
00:05:02,600 --> 00:05:03,600
He won't survive.

98
00:05:14,640 --> 00:05:15,570
You're injured.

99
00:05:16,320 --> 00:05:17,380
Where are you hurt?

100
00:05:18,360 --> 00:05:19,160
Don't move.

101
00:05:23,200 --> 00:05:24,200
I was outmatched.

102
00:05:24,680 --> 00:05:26,160
I'll take you to the hospital. Let's go.

103
00:05:26,160 --> 00:05:26,960
Don't move.

104
00:05:28,000 --> 00:05:28,920
It's too late.

105
00:05:36,000 --> 00:05:37,130
What I promised you,

106
00:05:38,520 --> 00:05:39,560
I did it.

107
00:05:41,600 --> 00:05:43,060
Information on Aunt Hong,

108
00:05:43,440 --> 00:05:44,560
I confirmed it.

109
00:05:46,000 --> 00:05:46,800
Take it.

110
00:05:50,520 --> 00:05:51,360
I'm sorry.

111
00:05:52,400 --> 00:05:53,720
If it weren't for me,

112
00:05:53,960 --> 00:05:55,960
asking you to investigate,

113
00:05:57,040 --> 00:05:59,560
they wouldn't have targeted you. I'm sorry.

114
00:06:00,760 --> 00:06:02,160
No matter who is to blame,

115
00:06:03,080 --> 00:06:04,240
it's not your fault.

116
00:06:08,360 --> 00:06:10,040
Let me tell you a secret.

117
00:06:19,960 --> 00:06:21,090
Aren't you curious?

118
00:06:22,680 --> 00:06:24,640
Why a mercenary man like me

119
00:06:25,480 --> 00:06:27,240
has been helping you?

120
00:06:28,880 --> 00:06:30,480
It wasn't just for the money.

121
00:06:31,920 --> 00:06:33,250
Your father, Zhu Zhang,

122
00:06:33,600 --> 00:06:36,080
was a generous and charitable man.

123
00:06:36,320 --> 00:06:38,880
He helped me when I was young.

124
00:06:40,200 --> 00:06:41,440
I owed him.

125
00:06:42,840 --> 00:06:43,900
I had to pay it back.

126
00:06:46,360 --> 00:06:48,240
Stop talking.

127
00:06:48,320 --> 00:06:49,450
Save your strength.

128
00:06:49,480 --> 00:06:50,480
I'm taking you to the hospital.

129
00:06:50,480 --> 00:06:51,520
You'll be fine.

130
00:06:51,520 --> 00:06:52,520
You're going to be okay.

131
00:06:52,520 --> 00:06:53,000
Alright?

132
00:06:53,000 --> 00:06:54,080
Don't bother.

133
00:06:55,840 --> 00:06:56,640
It's okay.

134
00:06:58,240 --> 00:07:00,080
I can die with no regrets.

135
00:07:05,040 --> 00:07:05,800
Look.

136
00:07:06,640 --> 00:07:08,280
The weather is so nice.

137
00:07:12,240 --> 00:07:13,320
What a pity.

138
00:07:16,120 --> 00:07:17,160
It's a shame.

139
00:08:06,360 --> 00:08:07,080
Young Marshal,

140
00:08:07,080 --> 00:08:07,680
the secret investigation you ordered last time

141
00:08:07,680 --> 00:08:09,480
has yielded results.

142
00:08:39,360 --> 00:08:41,320
You just recovered from your injury. Be careful.

143
00:08:41,320 --> 00:08:43,120
You're the center of attention today,

144
00:08:43,120 --> 00:08:44,780
and everyone is watching you.

145
00:08:46,040 --> 00:08:46,840
Let's go.

146
00:08:49,320 --> 00:08:50,120
Everyone,

147
00:08:51,000 --> 00:08:53,080
welcome to my humble abode.

148
00:08:55,400 --> 00:08:57,920
Shengsheng, I prepared this especially for you.

149
00:08:57,920 --> 00:08:58,680
Do you like it?

150
00:08:58,680 --> 00:09:00,320
It's beautiful. Thank you.

151
00:09:02,640 --> 00:09:03,320
Come.

152
00:09:04,880 --> 00:09:08,320
Everyone, please join me in wishing my beloved wife

153
00:09:08,480 --> 00:09:11,320
eternal youth and a happy birthday.

154
00:09:11,640 --> 00:09:13,560
Happy birthday.

155
00:09:15,760 --> 00:09:16,560
Happy birthday.

156
00:09:16,560 --> 00:09:17,720
Traitors

157
00:09:17,800 --> 00:09:18,360
must die.

158
00:09:19,440 --> 00:09:19,970
Huainan.

159
00:09:24,080 --> 00:09:25,200
After him!

160
00:09:25,400 --> 00:09:27,120
Shengsheng, are you okay?

161
00:09:27,240 --> 00:09:27,880
Huainan.

162
00:09:27,880 --> 00:09:29,960
Doctor! Get a doctor, quick!

163
00:09:29,960 --> 00:09:30,920
It hurts.
